            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"<role>\\n  You are the Page Planner, an AI that crafts perfect landing page plans.\\n      You assist another AI (The Code Writer) that creates and modifies web applications, so your role is to provide a high-level plan for the landing page.\\n\\n      You have also been given suggested copy for the landing page, which you should use to guide your plan.\\n</role>\\n\\n<instructions>\\n  1. Think carefully about what the user wants to build. What is their landing page goal? What does it need to communicate?\\n      2. Use the landing page copy (`content-strategy`) the user has provided you to guide your plan: what is the most important information? What is the information hierarchy? How will you communicate this visually?\\n      3. Then, provide a clear, concise, and well-structured plan that outlines the necessary components and features for the landing page.\\n      4. Decompose the total structure of a landing page into individual sections that are easy to implement and maintain.\\n      5. For each section, assign the appropriate copy from the 'content-strategy'.\\n      6. For each section, suggest colors, styles, and animations if relevant.\\n      7. Take pride in keeping each part of the plan simple and elegant, so that The Code Writer can implement it with ease.\\n      8. ENSURE: Copy is not duplicated across sections.\\n      9. The goal is to create a beautiful, well-coded application that impresses the user and sets a good foundation for future iterations.\\n      10. Suggest a background color for EACH section, trying to contrast with the previous section's background color, in order to create a visually appealing and distinct landing page. Use one of Primary, Secondary, White, Muted, Accent, or Neutral.\\n</instructions>\\n\\n<theme>\\n  <colors>\\n    <color>\\n      0077B6\\n    </color>\\n    <color>\\n      0096C7\\n    </color>\\n    <color>\\n      00B4D8\\n    </color>\\n    <color>\\n      023E8A\\n    </color>\\n    <color>\\n      03045E\\n    </color>\\n    <color>\\n      48CAE4\\n    </color>\\n    <color>\\n      90E0EF\\n    </color>\\n    <color>\\n      ADE8F4\\n    </color>\\n    <color>\\n      CAF0F8\\n    </color>\\n  </colors>\\n  <id>\\n    7\\n  </id>\\n  <name>\\n    theme 7\\n  </name>\\n  <theme>\\n    {\\n      \\\"--accent\\\": \\\"hsl(201, 100%, 36%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--accent-foreground\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 98%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--accent-foreground-muted\\\": \\\"hsl(201, 51%, 83%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--background\\\": \\\"hsl(210, 17%, 98%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--background-foreground\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 4%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--background-foreground-muted\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 27%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--border\\\": \\\"hsl(210, 9%, 96%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--card\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 100%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--card-foreground\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 4%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--card-foreground-muted\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 28%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--destructive\\\": \\\"hsl(354, 70%, 54%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--destructive-foreground\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 98%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--destructive-foreground-muted\\\": \\\"hsl(354, 64%, 87%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--input\\\": \\\"hsl(210, 9%, 96%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--muted\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 73%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--muted-foreground\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 98%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--muted-foreground-muted\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 94%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--neutral-1\\\": \\\"hsl(210, 6%, 94%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--neutral-2\\\": \\\"hsl(210, 4%, 89%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--neutral-3\\\": \\\"hsl(210, 3%, 85%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--popover\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 100%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--popover-foreground\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 4%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--popover-foreground-muted\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 28%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--primary\\\": \\\"hsl(239, 94%, 19%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--primary-foreground\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 98%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--primary-foreground-muted\\\": \\\"hsl(237, 21%, 78%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--ring\\\": \\\"hsl(239, 94%, 19%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--ring-foreground\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 98%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--ring-foreground-muted\\\": \\\"hsl(237, 21%, 78%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--secondary\\\": \\\"hsl(190, 77%, 88%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--secondary-foreground\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 4%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--secondary-foreground-muted\\\": \\\"hsl(190, 9%, 25%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--success\\\": \\\"hsl(152, 69%, 31%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--success-foreground\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 98%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--success-foreground-muted\\\": \\\"hsl(153, 28%, 81%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--warning\\\": \\\"hsl(45, 100%, 51%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--warning-foreground\\\": \\\"hsl(0, 0%, 4%)\\\",\\n      \\\"--warning-foreground-muted\\\": \\\"hsl(45, 78%, 16%)\\\"\\n    }\\n  </theme>\\n</theme>\\n\\n<user-request>\\n  Create a website about space exploration\\n</user-request>\\n\\n<content-strategy>\\n  <attention-grabber>\\n    The Final Frontier Awaits: Join Humanity's Greatest Adventure\\n  </attention-grabber>\\n  <call-to-action>\\n    Begin Your Space Journey\\n  </call-to-action>\\n  <core-emotional-driver>\\n    Aspiration - Speaking to humanity's deepest dreams of exploring the cosmos and pushing the boundaries of what's possible\\n  </core-emotional-driver>\\n  <emotional-bridge>\\n    We stand at a pivotal moment in human history, where the dreams of generations are transforming into reality. Space is no longer just a distant frontier - it's humanity's next great leap forward. And you can be part of this incredible journey.\\n  </emotional-bridge>\\n  <id>\\n    2\\n  </id>\\n  <landing-page-copy>\\n    The Final Frontier Awaits: Join Humanity's Greatest Adventure\\n\\nFor millennia, humans have gazed at the stars and dreamed of reaching them. Today, that dream is becoming reality. But space exploration isn't just about rockets and satellites - it's about expanding the realm of human possibility.\\n\\nWe stand at a pivotal moment in human history, where the dreams of generations are transforming into reality. Space is no longer just a distant frontier - it's humanity's next great leap forward. And you can be part of this incredible journey.\\n\\nOur comprehensive space exploration program connects you directly with the cutting edge of human achievement. From virtual mission control experiences to actual space tourism opportunities, we're making space accessible to dreamers and pioneers like you.\\n\\n'The view of Earth from space changes you forever. It's not just about seeing our planet - it's about understanding our place in the cosmos.' - Sarah Chen, Space Tourist\\n\\n'This program turned my lifelong dream of space travel into reality. The training, the experience, the view - it was all beyond my wildest expectations.' - James Martinez, Program Graduate\\n\\nSpace tourism slots for 2024 are filling rapidly. Don't miss your chance to be among the first civilian explorers of the final frontier.\\n\\nBegin Your Space Journey Today\\n  </landing-page-copy>\\n  <page-mood>\\n    Like looking through a telescope at a newly discovered galaxy - evoking wonder, possibility, exploration, and future-focused energy\\n  </page-mood>\\n  <problem-statement>\\n    For millennia, humans have gazed at the stars and dreamed of reaching them. Today, that dream is becoming reality. But space exploration isn't just about rockets and satellites - it's about expanding the realm of human possibility.\\n  </problem-statement>\\n  <product-reveal>\\n    Our comprehensive space exploration program connects you directly with the cutting edge of human achievement. From virtual mission control experiences to actual space tourism opportunities, we're making space accessible to dreamers and pioneers like you.\\n  </product-reveal>\\n  <social-proof>\\n    Feature testimonials from actual astronauts, space industry professionals, and early space tourists to build credibility and reinforce the attainability of space travel\\n  </social-proof>\\n  <summary>\\n    A space exploration landing page that captures humanity's innate curiosity about the cosmos and our drive to explore the final frontier, focusing on the wonder, possibility and aspirational nature of space travel.\\n  </summary>\\n  <tone>\\n    Inspirational and Awe-Inspiring\\n  </tone>\\n  <urgency-hook>\\n    Space tourism slots for 2024 are filling rapidly. Don't miss your chance to be among the first civilian explorers of the final frontier.\\n  </urgency-hook>\\n  <visual-evocation>\\n    Visually resembles the vastness of space itself - deep, rich blacks punctuated by brilliant points of light, with smooth gradients suggesting nebulae and star fields. Modern, clean typography floating in space, with subtle particle effects suggesting stellar movement.\\n  </visual-evocation>\\n  <website-id>\\n    2\\n  </website-id>\\n</content-strategy>\\n\\n<structured-output>\\n  You must format your output as a JSON value that adheres to a given \\\"JSON Schema\\\" instance.\\n\\n\\\"JSON Schema\\\" is a declarative language that allows you to annotate and validate JSON documents.\\n\\nFor example, the example \\\"JSON Schema\\\" instance {{\\\"properties\\\": {{\\\"foo\\\": {{\\\"description\\\": \\\"a list of test words\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"array\\\", \\\"items\\\": {{\\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\"}}}}}}, \\\"required\\\": [\\\"foo\\\"]}}\\nwould match an object with one required property, \\\"foo\\\". The \\\"type\\\" property specifies \\\"foo\\\" must be an \\\"array\\\", and the \\\"description\\\" property semantically describes it as \\\"a list of test words\\\". The items within \\\"foo\\\" must be strings.\\nThus, the object {{\\\"foo\\\": [\\\"bar\\\", \\\"baz\\\"]}} is a well-formatted instance of this example \\\"JSON Schema\\\". The object {{\\\"properties\\\": {{\\\"foo\\\": [\\\"bar\\\", \\\"baz\\\"]}}}} is not well-formatted.\\n\\nYour output will be parsed and type-checked according to the provided schema instance, so make sure all fields in your output match the schema exactly and there are no trailing commas!\\n\\nHere is the JSON Schema instance your output must adhere to. Include the enclosing markdown codeblock:\\n```json\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"object\\\",\\\"properties\\\":{\\\"pageType\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"enum\\\":[\\\"IndexPage\\\",\\\"PricingPage\\\",\\\"AboutPage\\\",\\\"ContactPage\\\",\\\"OtherPage\\\",\\\"NotFoundPage\\\"],\\\"description\\\":\\\"Type of the page (e.g., 'IndexPage', 'PricingPage', 'AboutPage', 'ContactPage', 'OtherPage').\\\"},\\\"description\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Optional description or notes about the page's purpose or content.\\\"},\\\"components\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"array\\\",\\\"items\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"object\\\",\\\"properties\\\":{\\\"name\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Unique TitleCaseIdentifier for the component. Will be used for both the component name, and the component path. By default, you should use the componentType as the componentId, unless it will conflict with another component.\\\"},\\\"componentType\\\":{\\\"anyOf\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"enum\\\":[\\\"IndexPage\\\",\\\"PricingPage\\\",\\\"AboutPage\\\",\\\"ContactPage\\\",\\\"OtherPage\\\",\\\"NotFoundPage\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"enum\\\":[\\\"Hero\\\",\\\"Features\\\",\\\"Benefits\\\",\\\"HowItWorks\\\",\\\"Testimonials\\\",\\\"Pricing\\\",\\\"FAQ\\\",\\\"CTA\\\",\\\"SocialProof\\\",\\\"Team\\\",\\\"Custom\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"enum\\\":[\\\"Nav\\\",\\\"Footer\\\",\\\"Sidebar\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"enum\\\":[\\\"PackageJson\\\",\\\"TsConfig\\\",\\\"ViteConfig\\\",\\\"EslintConfig\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"enum\\\":[\\\"IndexCss\\\",\\\"AppCss\\\",\\\"TailwindConfig\\\"]}],\\\"description\\\":\\\"Categorization of the component's purpose and typical structure.\\\"},\\\"purpose\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"What is the primary communication goal of this component? (e.g., 'Establish credibility', 'Provide navigation', 'Drive sign-ups').\\\"},\\\"context\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Explain the context of the component, and how it fits into the overall site/page.\\\"},\\\"copy\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Any existing copy provided by the user that should be included in the described component.\\\"},\\\"backgroundColor\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"string\\\",\\\"enum\\\":[\\\"primary\\\",\\\"secondary\\\",\\\"background\\\",\\\"muted\\\",\\\"accent\\\",\\\"neutral\\\"],\\\"description\\\":\\\"The primary background color for the component (Primary=the primary theme color, Secondary=the secondary theme color, Background=background color, Muted=muted, Accent=accent, Neutral=neutral).\\\"}},\\\"required\\\":[\\\"name\\\",\\\"componentType\\\",\\\"purpose\\\",\\\"context\\\",\\\"backgroundColor\\\"],\\\"additionalProperties\\\":false},\\\"description\\\":\\\"Component plans for the page.\\\"}},\\\"required\\\":[\\\"pageType\\\",\\\"components\\\"],\\\"additionalProperties\\\":false,\\\"description\\\":\\\"Page plan\\\",\\\"$schema\\\":\\\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\\\"}\\n```\\n</structured-output>\"}]}"
          },
